data.description: TAKE OVER SELLERS MONTHLY PAYMENTS OF $1,442.31 PITI AT 3% INTEREST RATE & $115.00 FOR SECOND MORTGAGE AT 6% VIA SUBTO, $67K DOWN PAYMENT WILL BE REQUIRED AT CLOSINGS!! Welcome to your tranquil 3-bed, 2-bath ranch-style home on a spacious, flat lot with a timeless 4 sided brick exterior. This residence boasts a two-car carport, and its roof, HVAC, and water heater were all updated in 2016 for worry-free living.    Step inside to an inviting floor plan, highlighted by a vaulted-ceiling family room, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. The well-appointed kitchen & upgraded bathroom vanities. The master bedroom offers two closets for ample storage.    With a total of 3 bedrooms and 2 well-maintained bathrooms, this home is perfect for family living. Outside, the large corner lot provides space for outdoor activities.    Located in charming Bombing Newnan, just 10 minutes from downtown Newnan, this beautifully updated home won't last long. Welcome to a life of comfort, convenience, and endless possibilities!
